178
00:13:02,641 --> 00:13:03,783
Again, it's

179
00:13:05,650 --> 00:13:16,277
When you talk about community, what happened the other evening with the reverse 911, social media, the police officers and fire department.

180
00:13:16,697 --> 00:13:22,761
I mean, people just rallying around trying to find this person in need that was walking around.

181
00:13:22,801 --> 00:13:25,923
And I'm going to toot my own daughter's horn that

182
00:13:26,463 --> 00:13:34,305
