183
00:13:34,705 --> 00:13:40,486
Do I mind if her and her friends would walk the neighborhood to see if they can help?

184
00:13:40,886 --> 00:13:48,408
And I think that just wasn't my daughter, but people in general really came out of their homes and instead of walking a daily walk one way, people walked.

185
00:13:48,808 --> 00:13:55,671
