307
00:22:32,162 --> 00:22:39,886
So I think that what we need to do is budget meetings so we can actually have a nice conversation that is full of information.

308
00:22:40,126 --> 00:22:44,328
And if there's items that we need to follow up on or they need to follow up on, that's fine.

309
00:22:44,348 --> 00:22:46,949
We're not doing it last minute in June.

310
00:22:47,609 --> 00:22:53,772
So therefore, I would ask if you could please schedule budget meetings, maybe two or three a month.

311
00:22:56,332 --> 00:22:58,693
Starting in February would be ideal.

312
00:22:59,493 --> 00:23:06,255
